        "content": "## Terraform plan: upgrade analytics DB\n\n**PR:** platform/terraform#482  \u00b7  **Author:** data-platform@  \u00b7  **Target:** prod\n\nUpgrading the analytics warehouse from a single `db.r6g.large` to a 3-node\n`db.r6g.4xlarge` Aurora cluster to handle Q4 forecasted load (3\u00d7 ingest, 2\u00d7 query\nconcurrency).\n\n```hcl\n- resource \"aws_rds_cluster\" \"analytics\" {\n-   cluster_identifier = \"analytics\"\n-   engine             = \"aurora-postgresql\"\n-   engine_version     = \"15.4\"\n-   instance_class     = \"db.r6g.large\"   # 2 vCPU, 16 GB\n-   instances          = 1\n-   storage_encrypted  = true\n- }\n\n+ resource \"aws_rds_cluster\" \"analytics_v2\" {\n+   cluster_identifier = \"analytics-v2\"\n+   engine             = \"aurora-postgresql\"\n+   engine_version     = \"16.2\"\n+   instance_class     = \"db.r6g.4xlarge\"  # 16 vCPU, 128 GB\n+   instances          = 3\n+   storage_encrypted  = true\n+   deletion_protection = false\n+ }\n```\n\nCutover plan: snapshot old cluster \u2192 restore into new \u2192 45-min DNS swap \u2192\ndelete old cluster after 7-day verification window.\n",
